href=\"./Mathlib/Data/Set/Defs.html#setOf\">}</a></span> <a href=\"./Init/Prelude.html#Eq\">=</a> <span class=\"fn\">(↑<span class=\"fn\">m</span>)</span><a href=\"./Init/Prelude.html#Inv.inv\">⁻¹</a></div></div>","info":{"doc":"The Schnirelmann density of the set of naturals which are `1 mod m` is `m⁻¹`, for any `m ≠ 1`.\n\nNote that if `m = 1`, this set is empty.\n","docLink":"./Mathlib/Combinatorics/Schnirelmann.html#schnirelmannDensity_setOf_mod_eq_one","kind":"theorem","line":219,"name":"schnirelmannDensity_setOf_mod_eq_one","sourceLink":"https://github.com/leanprover-community/mathlib4/blob/087469e24922b85cb737497c74556c7dacc01f22/Mathlib/Combinatorics/Schnirelmann.lean#L219-L257"}},{"header":"<div class=\"decl_header\"><span class=\"decl_kind\">theorem</span>\n<span class=\"decl_name\"><a class=\"break_within\" href=\"./Mathlib/Combinatorics/Schnirelmann.html#schnirelmannDensity_setOf_prime\"><span class=\"name\">schnirelmannDensity_setOf_prime</span></a></span><span class=\"decl_args\"> :</span><div class=\"decl_type\"><span class=\"fn\"><a href=\"./Mathlib/Combinatorics/Schnirelmann.html#schnirelmannDensity\">schnirelmannDensity</a> <span class=\"fn\">(<a href=\"./Mathlib/Data/Set/Defs.html#setOf\">setOf</a> <a href=\"./Mathlib/Data/Nat/Prime/Defs.html#Nat.Prime\">Nat.Prime</a>)</span></span> <a href=\"./Init/Prelude.html#Eq\">=</a> <span class=\"fn\">0</span></div></div>","info":{"doc":"","docLink":"./Mathlib/Combinatorics/Schnirelmann.html#schnirelmannDensity_setOf_prime","kind":"theorem","line":216,"name":"schnirelmannDensity_setOf_prime","sourceLink":"https://github.com/leanprover-community/mathlib4/blob/087469e24922b85cb737497c74556c7dacc01f22/Mathlib/Combinatorics/Schnirelmann.lean#L216-L217"}},{"header":"<div class=\"decl_header\"><span class=\"decl_kind\">theorem</span>\n<span class=\"decl_name\"><a class=\"break_within\" href=\"./Mathlib/Combinatorics/Schnirelmann.html#schnirelmannDensity_setOf_even\"><span class=\"name\">schnirelmannDensity_setOf_